  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK680">
<l>uṟaiciṟiyā ruṇṇaṭuṅka lañcik kuṟaipeṟiṟ </l>
<l>koḷvar periyārp paṇintu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Ministers of small states, afraid of their people being frightened, will yield to and acknowledge their superior foes, if the latter offer them a chance of reconciliation</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
